the cancer doesn't spread anymore.

24
00:00:58,160 --> 00:01:01,170
We thought that this method
would be better,

25
00:01:01,230 --> 00:01:03,070
and then do the surgery
after seeing the results.

26
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:05,970
Please do your best.

27
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:07,510
Of course.

28
