Why would you die?

31
00:01:24,490 --> 00:01:25,690
That won't happen.

32
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,290
Didn't you hear
the hospital director?

33
00:01:27,630 --> 00:01:29,290
He said the cancer has spread
throughout my body.

34
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:34,000
Well, it's just a little
around your stomach.

35
00:01:35,170 --> 00:01:37,300
Please don't have
any negative thoughts...

36
00:01:37,470 --> 00:01:39,240
and focus on your treatment.

37
00:01:40,410 --> 00:01:42,540
You will live.

38
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:48,150
I'll help you fully recover.

39
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:53,320
I'd rather die than go to prison.

40
00:01:54,190 --> 00:01:56,190
I'll refuse
to receive any treatment.

41
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,190
Honey.

42
00:01:58,190 --> 00:01:59,360
Once I die,

43
00:01:59,820 --> 00:02:02,060
