to feel guilty, too.

44
00:02:04,330 --> 00:02:06,460
You tortured me
for the last 30 years.

45
00:02:07,030 --> 00:02:09,230
How could my body and mind
have remained healthy?

46
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,170
You ruined me.

47
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:16,010
The more I see you,
the more pain I feel in my body,

48
