71
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,650
I would've done the same...

72
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,320
if this were my daughter's business.

73
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,660
I was jealous of her,
but I began to feel bad.

74
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:57,900
That woman, Choi Ja Young, doesn't
hesitate to use money and power...

75
00:04:58,370 --> 00:05:00,000
to attack, blackmail,
and even murder someone.

76
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,970
She'll do anything.

77
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:05,340
She took another woman's life
like it meant nothing,

78
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:08,150
just to protect
her only daughter's happiness.

79
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:10,820
Your sister's life...

80
00:05:11,180 --> 00:05:13,450
came to nothing
because of Kang Jae In.

81
00:05:16,690 --> 00:05:17,990
You want to enjoy your life...

82
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:20,190
in the VIP ward
without paying for what you did?

83
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:23,700
Does she have no remorse...

84
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:26,060
for my sister's unfair death?

85
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,000
My niece lost her mother,

86
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,540
and my mom lost her daughter.
They struggle to keep living.

87
00:05:34,510 --> 00:05:37,180
Choi Ja Young, you're pure evil.

88
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:40,980
If the law cannot punish you,
I'll do it myself.

89
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,350
Watch and see
how your dear daughter...

90
00:05:45,150 --> 00:05:46,950
crashes and falls.

91
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,390
I'll destroy her happiness,

92
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,860
the very thing
you wanted to protect.

93
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,400
Hello? It's me, Uncle.

94
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:03,370
I need your help.

95
00:06:09,610 --> 00:06:10,980
Hey, you're here.

96
00:06:11,110 --> 00:06:12,180
Hey.

97
00:06:13,810 --> 00:06:14,950
Have you heard?

98
00:06:15,150 --> 00:06:17,320
Director Choi Ja Young
was hospitalized.

99
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,850
Hospitalized? Here?

100
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,890
Yes, she has cancer.

101
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:24,320
I heard it was either stage 3 or 4.

102
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:28,730
So, you didn't know?

103
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,860
Shouldn't you tell your friend?

104
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,430
Those above kept it confidential
to keep this on the down low,

105
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,600
so she might have no idea.

106
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:36,530
You're right.

107
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:44,240
Hello? Hey, Jae In. It's me.

108
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,610
Can you come to the hospital?

109
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:48,350
Yes, okay.

110
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:52,320
She's on her way here.

111
00:06:53,050 --> 00:06:54,820
Is that so? That's good.

112
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:58,490
Bye, then. Have a good day.

113
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,090
Hey, it's Kang Jae In!

114
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:02,460
- Ms. Kang!
- Are you Ms. Kang?

115
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:03,530
Was your mother,
Director Choi Ja Young, detained...

116
00:07:03,530 --> 00:07:05,260
for attempted murder
in a hit-and-run accident?

117
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:07,400
Is it true that she forged
her medical document...

118
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:10,400
for stomach cancer to be suspended
from her detainment?

119
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:12,600
Is your father,
Chairman Kang Gyu Cheol, aware of this?

120
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,570
Did Chairman Kang
exert his influence...

121
00:07:14,570 --> 00:07:16,510
to suspend Ms. Choi's detainment?

122
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:18,440
Did he abuse the justice system?

123
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:20,240
- Please explain, Ms. Kang!
- Ms. Kang.

124
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,610
- Ms. Kang!
- Please explain the situation.

125
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:23,480
- Say something, Ms. Kang!
- Are the allegations true?

126
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,150
Please wait. Please.

127
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:28,150
Ms. Kang!

128
00:07:33,690 --> 00:07:35,090
- Ms. Kang!
- Goodness. Is she okay?

129
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:38,400
Hey.

130
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,100
Are you okay?

131
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:44,900
Yes, I'm fine.

132
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:46,940
Thank you.

133
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:51,280
I'll handle the situation here.
You should go.

134
00:07:52,810 --> 00:07:53,880
Okay.

135
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:59,180
I told you
not to let the information leak out.

136
00:07:59,450 --> 00:08:00,690
Why won't you do your job?

137
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,490
If you can't keep your employees
under control,

138
00:08:03,490 --> 00:08:05,160
how am I going to trust you
and continue as a sponsor?

139
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:06,960
I'm sorry.

140
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,490
You run your hospital...

141
00:08:08,490 --> 00:08:10,630
with the annual contribution
YL Group makes.

142
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,660
If this is how you'll do your job,

143
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:15,900
we'll call off the agreement
to sponsor the cancer center.

144
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:24,310
Find out who the whistleblower is.

145
00:08:24,910 --> 00:08:26,040
You may leave.

146
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:35,090
Come on in.

147
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,490
I thought you weren't well.

148
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:43,900
Do you want me to be unwell?

149
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,300
Mom.

150
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:47,330
I'm unwell. I'm quite unwell.

151
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:49,970
My only daughter is
refusing to see me.

152
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,570
How can I be well?

153
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,340
I was asking...

154
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,710
if you had stomach cancer.

155
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:57,910
Be honest with me.

156
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:00,010
Do you really have stomach cancer?

157
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:07,920
So, the reporters were
all telling the truth.

158
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:10,760
You don't have to mind
whatever they say.

159
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,260
Just ignore them.

160
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:13,760
You're too cowardly.

161
00:09:14,730 --> 00:09:17,560
I knew you had elitism
and a sense of entitlement,

162
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:20,060
but I still thought
you were a great woman.

163
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,100
You were confident and dignified
wherever you went,

164
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,640
and you seemed honorable.

165
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:29,170
But those were just elitism...

166
00:09:29,470 --> 00:09:30,840
and your sense of entitlement.

167
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:33,950
Those things are
not important right now, Jae In.

168
00:09:34,580 --> 00:09:37,210
What's really important is that
you must secure your place.

169
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:40,150
And to do that,
you must pull out the weeds.

170
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,650
Mom.

171
00:09:43,350 --> 00:09:44,990
Yes, Jae In.
You need to listen to me.

172
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,720
First, divorce Gi Chan.

173
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,730
That's the best move
you can make for yourself.

174
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:51,330
I'll do anything for you.

175
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:52,900
Do you understand?

176
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,870
I'm pregnant.

177
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:00,500
Abort it now.

178
00:10:02,210 --> 00:10:03,980
How can you say that?

179
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,680
You need to wake up, Jae In.

180
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,410
Face the reality.

181
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:09,850
I know he's having an affair.

182
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:14,120
- You're delusional.
- I'd rather it be a delusion.

183
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:17,390
But I'm sorry.
I saw it with my own two eyes.

184
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:21,460
I can still picture
the photos I saw on your phone.

185
00:10:22,730 --> 00:10:23,860
Photos?

186
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:26,730
The other woman sent those to you
as if she wanted you to see them.

187
00:10:27,730 --> 00:10:29,130
I don't even want to speak of it.

188
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:31,640
I thought
you'd be shocked to see those,

189
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:33,540
so I deleted the message.

190
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:37,580
I didn't want you to live like me.

191
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:40,380
I wanted you to be happy.

192
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,650
Is that wrong?

193
00:10:43,780 --> 00:10:45,320
You keep saying
you'll do anything for me,

194
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,220
but I just don't get it,
no matter how hard I try.

195
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:51,220
Why didn't you tell me back then?

196
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:53,590
This is all your selfishness.

197
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,460
And I don't plan
to break up my family...

198
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,100
because of that.

199
00:10:58,730 --> 00:11:01,400
I will not divorce him.

200
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:05,600
You're stabbing yourself
in the back.

201
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:09,810
Go back into detention
and get tried.

202
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:13,140
That's what you need to do
if you really will do anything for me.

203
00:11:13,610 --> 00:11:15,010
And come back to me...

204
00:11:15,810 --> 00:11:17,050
when you can stand tall again.

205
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,650
Please do that, Mom.

206
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,620
I don't need a daughter
who doesn't want her mother.

207
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:26,420
I don't care
for either you or your father.

208
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:28,160
Goodbye.

209
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:45,680
Goodness.

210
00:11:50,650 --> 00:11:53,750
Gi Chan, I'm in your office.
Where are you?

211
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,750
Why did you come without calling me?

212
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:57,190
I'm busy right now.

213
00:11:57,720 --> 00:12:00,390
I came because I couldn't discuss this
at home.

214
00:12:01,290 --> 00:12:04,060
What happened between you
and Jae In's friend?

215
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:05,860
Did you end it with her?

216
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,900
You'll have your second child, so...

217
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,470
Hello?

218
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:16,510
Gosh, he's driving me crazy.

219
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,680
What if Jae In finds out?

220
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:26,850
Goodness, Ms. Noh. Hello.

221
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:29,820
Director Hwang isn't here.

222
00:12:30,290 --> 00:12:32,590
Why don't you have a seat?

223
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,990
I'll call him.

224
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:38,030
You evil brat.
How dare you walk in here?

225
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:40,360
How dare you seduce him?

226
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:42,500
- What are you doing?
- How can you hit on...

227
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:43,830
your friend's husband?

228
00:12:43,830 --> 00:12:45,240
You evil brat.

229
00:12:45,470 --> 00:12:47,100
Ms. Noh!

230
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:52,910
The person you have reached
is unavailable. Please...

231
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:55,180
He won't pick up his phone.

232
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:57,750
Ms. Noh?

233
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:00,450
If I made a scene at work, then...

234
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:06,220
I'd like to speak with you quietly
outside of the office.

235
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,790
When can you do that?

236
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:11,900
Actually, I prepared
a present for you.

237
00:13:12,730 --> 00:13:14,030
Should I come to your place later?

238
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:23,010
Meet me here after work.

239
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:25,280
Okay, Ms. Noh.

240
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:33,920
What can I say to her
to scare her out of her wits?

241
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:36,290
I can already tell...

242
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:39,060
that she's not an easy girl
to deal with.

243
00:13:42,090 --> 00:13:43,260
Ms. Noh.

244
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:52,740
This is a present for you.
I got you a bag.

245
00:13:53,970 --> 00:13:56,110
It's made with crocodile leather,
and it's a limited edition.

246
00:13:56,110 --> 00:13:57,210
I don't want it.

247
00:13:57,880 --> 00:14:00,710
I don't know what your story is,

248
00:14:01,110 --> 00:14:02,580
but you got the wrong person.

249
00:14:03,050 --> 00:14:04,150
Ms. Noh.

250
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:06,750
Shut your mouth!
Stop acting so friendly.

251
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:10,290
You make it impossible
for me to be nice.

252
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:11,560
How can you seduce...

253
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:13,420
your friend's husband
and keep him as another man?

254
00:14:13,990 --> 00:14:15,490
If you want to have an affair,
do it with someone else!

255
00:14:15,930 --> 00:14:16,990
Goodness.

256
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:20,460
Ms. Noh, it's not an affair.
We're in love.

257
00:14:20,930 --> 00:14:23,100
Gi Chan and I are in love.

258
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:27,000
Haven't you heard?
Jae In is pregnant.

259
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:28,710
Would he do that if he loved you?

260
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:31,280
Well, that can happen.

261
00:14:31,780 --> 00:14:34,780
What's more important is that
his heart is with me.

262
00:14:35,450 --> 00:14:36,980
Stop talking nonsense.

263
00:14:37,310 --> 00:14:39,350
You're so shameless.

264
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:41,190
I've never seen
another married woman...

265
00:14:41,190 --> 00:14:42,890
as brazen as you.

266
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:46,160
Hey, does your husband know
you're out here doing this?

267
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,860
Would you like to meet my husband?

268
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:51,230
He's someone
you know better than anyone.

269
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:52,960
What?

270
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:55,730
I want to get along with you,
Ms. Noh.

271
00:14:56,570 --> 00:14:58,700
Mom, I got all these.

272
00:14:58,700 --> 00:14:59,840
What do I do now?

273
00:15:04,810 --> 00:15:06,040
- Ms. Noh!
- Goodness, Mom!

274
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,550
Ms. Noh.

275
00:15:08,550 --> 00:15:09,710
This is my answer.

276
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,680
You are like...

277
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:13,720
these discarded bones to my son.

278
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:16,290
How long do you think
he'll gnaw on the bone...

279
00:15:16,290 --> 00:15:18,420
instead of perfectly good meat?

280
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:20,420
Learn your place and get lost...

281
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,890
before I throw you into a trash can.

282
00:15:22,430 --> 00:15:23,760
You'll never win against me.

283
00:15:24,090 --> 00:15:25,430
Today was just the beginning.

284
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:28,570
You know what to do
if you don't want this to be worse.

285
00:15:30,470 --> 00:15:33,200
Ms. Noh, please excuse me today.

286
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,770
I hope to meet you
with a smile next time.

287
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:38,110
Have you gone crazy?

288
00:15:38,110 --> 00:15:40,010
- Mom, you need to stop.
- You!

289
00:15:40,010 --> 00:15:41,980
You have to stop, Mom.

290
00:15:42,610 --> 00:15:45,220
If you go out,
the neighbors might see this.

291
00:15:46,620 --> 00:15:48,990
It'll take a while
to get rid of that girl.

292
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:52,920
I'll return this to her.

293
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:55,030
Why would you do that?

294
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,460
