Here.

314
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,600
Goodness.

315
00:17:10,730 --> 00:17:12,770
You don't have to do this.

316
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:18,880
Please.

317
00:17:27,450 --> 00:17:28,550
Thank you.

318
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,890
