And our office phone will
ring off the hook, too.

322
00:17:41,470 --> 00:17:42,670
We can't patch this up.

323
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,640
We'll find a way
to reduce damages to YL Group.

324
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:48,940
Is Ja Young out of her mind?

325
00:17:49,710 --> 00:17:51,840
I know she grew up
as a snobby princess,

326
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:53,710
but doesn't she know
what the world has become?

327
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:55,350
How can she do this?

328
00:17:56,380 --> 00:17:57,880
Let's discuss this tomorrow.

329
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:02,290
We have to persuade Mom
and send her back to jail.

330
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,920
We should.

331
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:13,900
What is it?
What's taking you so long?

332
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:15,170
What is it?

333
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:18,100
It's about the culprit
who killed Do Hee.

334
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:20,570
She faked her medical diagnosis
and got hospitalized.

335
00:18:20,970 --> 00:18:23,440
I told reporters about it,
and it'd be on the news tonight.

336
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:27,110
Great job. Good call.

337
00:18:27,340 --> 00:18:29,110
The world needs to know.

338
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:31,320
And about Do Hee.

339
00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:34,020
That woman killed her...

340
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:37,020
because she thought her son-in-law
was having an affair with Do Hee.

341
