Do Hee was his other woman?

345
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,970
That's impossible.

346
00:18:55,110 --> 00:18:56,510
- No.
- You're right.

347
00:18:57,410 --> 00:18:58,780
It can't be Do Hee.

348
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:02,080
I don't know if she's mistaken
or misunderstanding,

349
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,710
but it wasn't Do Hee.

350
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:08,290
I wanted to keep it a secret,

351
00:19:08,290 --> 00:19:11,020
but I didn't want you to be shocked
after seeing the news.

352
00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:13,490
The media had to catch the story
to stir the public's interest...

353
00:19:13,490 --> 00:19:15,660
and have her punished
for what she did.

354
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:17,900
We should do that.

355
00:19:19,930 --> 00:19:21,000
Yes.

356
00:19:22,530 --> 00:19:24,030
She must be punished.

357
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:27,070
The wife of a corporate chairman is
currently detained...

358
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:29,210
and under investigation
for a hit-and-run case.

359
00:19:29,210 --> 00:19:30,770
She reportedly received
a false medical diagnosis...

360
00:19:30,770 --> 00:19:32,740
and was hospitalized
in the VIP ward of this hospital,

361
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:35,480
only to continue living in luxury.

362
00:19:35,650 --> 00:19:36,850
What's more serious is that...

363
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:38,750
the incident
may not have been a simple accident.

364
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:40,120
It is alleged that...

365
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:42,290
she mistook the victim
for her son-in-law's mistress...

366
00:19:42,290 --> 00:19:44,820
and struck her intentionally
with her car.

367
00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:50,660
I'm sorry, Mother.

368
00:19:51,700 --> 00:19:53,500
You don't have to apologize,

369
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:56,030
but she should've been punished
for what she did wrong.

370
00:19:56,230 --> 00:19:58,900
She tried to pull a trick
but humiliated the family.

371
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,910
This doesn't feel so great.

372
00:20:02,870 --> 00:20:03,970
An affair?

373
00:20:03,970 --> 00:20:06,210
That's enough.
Don't make this harder for Jae In.

374
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:08,580
Let's go.

375
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:14,990
Mom, is this true?

376
00:20:15,290 --> 00:20:17,490
She killed the woman,
thinking Gi Chan was having an affair?

377
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:18,920
I don't know. Be quiet.

378
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,320
You're all dismissed.

379
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:29,170
He was so lucky.

380
00:20:32,170 --> 00:20:34,970
Gosh, my mom should be an actress.

381
00:20:34,970 --> 00:20:36,940
She could've made it in Hollywood
with that talent.

382
00:20:36,940 --> 00:20:38,480
She's very good.

383
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:42,680
How's the pig's feet restaurant
working out? Is it doable?

384
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:44,780
Why are you asking me
about pig's feet now?

385
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:47,880
Don't take me as a joke
just because I sell pig's feet.

386
00:20:47,950 --> 00:20:50,620
You should be grateful
for a husband like me.

387
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:52,820
I never cheat.
I only have my eyes on you.

388
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:55,490
Gi Chan only has
his eyes on Jae In, too.

389
00:20:58,260 --> 00:20:59,430
Don't tell anyone,

390
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:01,200
but Gi Chan had an affair.

391
00:21:01,330 --> 00:21:02,700
It's still going on.

392
00:21:03,470 --> 00:21:04,870
Stop lying,

393
00:21:04,870 --> 00:21:07,240
pull yourself together,
and make your business work out.

394
00:21:08,470 --> 00:21:11,110
Hey, why won't you believe me?

395
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:15,080
All right.
It's better that you don't know.

396
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:17,480
It'll only blow up
if Jae In hears about it.

397
00:21:17,610 --> 00:21:18,680
That's true.

398
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:20,550
I need to find beer.

399
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,470
You're drinking again?

400
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:41,040
You'll hurt yourself
if you keep doing this every day.

401
00:21:41,410 --> 00:21:42,470
You need to stop drinking.

402
00:22:27,450 --> 00:22:29,620
What? I thought you just left.

403
00:22:29,820 --> 00:22:31,690
I just heard the front door.

404
00:22:38,500 --> 00:22:39,860
This area isn't for just anybody.

405
00:22:40,330 --> 00:22:42,800
Just anybody?

406
00:22:43,800 --> 00:22:46,640
There's a murder inside,
so why can't I go there?

407
00:22:47,170 --> 00:22:49,140
Move aside.

408
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:51,170
(VIP Ward)

409
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,880
Bring my daughter back.

410
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:56,010
Bring my poor daughter back.

411
00:22:58,150 --> 00:22:59,820
How can you do this?

412
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:03,220
How can you shamelessly be there
after taking someone's life?

413
00:23:03,290 --> 00:23:04,620
How?

414
00:23:04,890 --> 00:23:07,660
You're a murderer.
Bring my daughter back.

415
00:23:08,660 --> 00:23:11,530
Bring my poor Do Hee back!

416
00:23:11,530 --> 00:23:12,600
You need to stop.

417
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:14,060
If you keep doing this,
we'll call the police.

418
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:22,040
Bring my daughter back.

419
00:23:23,870 --> 00:23:28,710
Excuse me.
Are you Ms. Kim Do Hee's mother?

420
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:34,720
I am the culprit's husband.

421
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:38,490
I sincerely apologize.

422
00:23:42,390 --> 00:23:43,560
Bring my daughter back.

423
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:45,960
Bring my poor daughter back.

424
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,500
Bring her back.

425
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:49,730
- Please stop.
- Bring my poor Do Hee back!

426
00:23:49,730 --> 00:23:51,870
- Bring her back!
- Ma'am, please.

427
00:23:52,040 --> 00:23:53,800
- Goodness.
- Mr. Chairman!

428
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,670
- Call Dr. Park. Now!
- Yes, sir.

429
00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:57,470
Mr. Chairman!

430
00:23:57,770 --> 00:24:01,280
Bring my daughter back...

431
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,410
Mom!

432
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:08,050
My daughter...

433
00:24:08,850 --> 00:24:11,350
My poor daughter.

434
00:24:11,350 --> 00:24:14,220
My Do Hee...

435
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:15,660
My...

436
00:24:17,230 --> 00:24:20,800
How can the justice system
still favor the rich in the 21st century?

437
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:22,730
- How can this be?
- How can this be?

438
00:24:22,730 --> 00:24:25,770
The judiciary must stop kneeling
before money and power!

439
00:24:25,770 --> 00:24:27,500
- Stop kneeling!
- Stop kneeling!

440
00:24:27,500 --> 00:24:29,770
The judiciary does not work
for YL Group as a subcontractor!

441
00:24:29,770 --> 00:24:32,340
- Wake up!
- Wake up!

442
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:35,550
How can the justice system
still favor the rich in the 21st century?

443
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,310
- How can this be?
- How can this be?

444
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:40,250
The judiciary must stop kneeling
before money and power!

445
00:24:40,250 --> 00:24:41,850
- Stop kneeling!
- Stop kneeling!

446
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:43,550
There is a strong public backlash.

447
00:24:44,690 --> 00:24:46,590
The case turned into a social issue,

448
00:24:47,020 --> 00:24:49,660
and people quickly put together
a boycott against YL Group.

449
00:24:50,130 --> 00:24:51,760
Many people are demanding...

450
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:54,260
that they return products
they've already purchased.

451
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:57,700
Following that,
our stock price plummeted, too.

452
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:00,500
She framed one of the employees
as an adulteress and killed her.

453
00:25:00,500 --> 00:25:02,070
If that wasn't enough,
she pulled a trick...

454
00:25:02,570 --> 00:25:05,010
in an attempt to suspend
her detention,

455
00:25:05,140 --> 00:25:06,610
and the news is
all over the Internet.

456
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:10,450
The image we established
as a corporation...

457
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:12,180
completely crashed
because of Ja Young.

458
00:25:12,580 --> 00:25:15,750
There's also a protest
in front of our headquarters office.

459
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:19,460
Have you thought of countermeasures?

460
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:24,230
We should draw a line
between Mother and the business...

461
00:25:25,560 --> 00:25:28,270
to avoid the responsibility
as much as possible.

462
00:25:28,770 --> 00:25:29,870
Draw a line?

463
00:25:30,570 --> 00:25:32,300
Are you telling me to divorce her?

464
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:35,640
If that's what you must do
to improve YL's image,

465
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:37,210
then that's the right thing to do.

466
00:25:37,970 --> 00:25:40,710
A business shouldn't be tied
to a murderer and a criminal.

467
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:46,950
What if I forsake
my management rights?

468
00:25:47,650 --> 00:25:48,690
Gyu Cheol.

469
00:25:48,690 --> 00:25:51,390
It'd seem irresponsible
if I divorced her...

470
00:25:51,390 --> 00:25:53,160
in this situation.

471
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:56,790
After all, we're married,
and we're family.

472
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:59,460
If I divorce her
because of a disadvantage,

473
00:26:00,430 --> 00:26:02,870
it'll only seem like a deception.

474
00:26:03,500 --> 00:26:06,600
Also, I'm partially responsible
for this.

475
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:11,270
Let's send her back
to the detention center,

476
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:15,280
and I'll step down
as soon as possible.

477
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:19,650
Who do you have in mind
as your successor?

478
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:22,890
Will it be Seung Woo? Or...

479
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:27,190
Let's discuss that later.

480
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,360
I told you ages ago
to find the whistleblower...

481
00:26:30,730 --> 00:26:33,430
and bring him to me,
so what's taking you so long?

482
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:36,270
Even if reporters found out
about the fake medical report,

483
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,600
you should've insisted...

484
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,870
that it was wrong
and that no mistakes were made.

485
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,370
What do you think you're doing?

486
00:26:42,270 --> 00:26:45,180
Do you think you'll live
after betraying me like this?

487
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:48,210
I'm doing my best to find out.

488
00:26:48,450 --> 00:26:51,010
Make an official statement
that the news reports are all false.

489
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:53,520
Tell them someone at your hospital
made a false report...

490
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,680
with malicious intent.

491
00:26:57,050 --> 00:26:59,560
There's no need to do that.
You may leave.

492
00:27:02,130 --> 00:27:03,560
Didn't you hear me?

493
00:27:11,170 --> 00:27:13,000
You should've been getting ready
to return to the detention center...

494
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,270
as soon as you got notified.

495
00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:15,810
Will you stand here like this?

496
00:27:16,170 --> 00:27:17,510
You seem excited.

497
00:27:18,210 --> 00:27:21,010
Are you that happy to know
that I'll be detained again?

498
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:22,880
It's just as you said.

499
00:27:23,410 --> 00:27:25,850
I'm the problem
that caused this situation,

500
00:27:26,020 --> 00:27:27,720
and I brought it upon myself.

501
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:32,060
You can blame me
and resent me all you want,

502
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:35,430
but don't end up
hurting Jae In, too.

503
00:27:35,530 --> 00:27:37,930
You're her mom.

504
00:27:38,560 --> 00:27:41,200
You didn't just kill Ms. Kim.

505
00:27:41,430 --> 00:27:45,140
You also trampled on
the trust your daughter had in you,

506
00:27:45,540 --> 00:27:48,170
and this recent incident
destroyed her trust even more.

507
00:27:49,340 --> 00:27:52,440
Stop making up an excuse
to blame this on me.

508
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:55,780
You and Hwang Gi Chan
provided the reason.

509
00:27:56,350 --> 00:27:58,280
You two are truly evil.

510
00:27:59,080 --> 00:28:00,380
You need to get ready.

511
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:02,620
I'm a patient,

512
00:28:03,290 --> 00:28:04,850
and I'm here to receive treatment.

513
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,460
Not you,

514
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:09,730
not anyone in this country
has the right to stop me.

515
00:28:10,290 --> 00:28:13,260
The more you go on,
the more you'll hurt Jae In.

516
00:28:13,860 --> 00:28:16,270
Do you not care about the gossip
that's printed out every day...

517
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:17,800
about her?

518
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:20,000
Sue all of them for defamation.

519
00:28:20,500 --> 00:28:22,270
You're the one...

520
00:28:22,610 --> 00:28:24,370
who ruined Jae In's reputation.

521
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,810
Let me leave you with this.

522
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:31,880
If you want to get
Jae In's forgiveness,

523
00:28:32,250 --> 00:28:33,620
go back to the detention center...

524
00:28:33,820 --> 00:28:35,690
and stay there quietly
until your trial.

525
00:28:36,350 --> 00:28:38,620
Don't make this worse
and let her see you get dragged.

526
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,180
My gosh.

527
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:04,380
Did I surprise you?

528
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:05,680
Of course, I was surprised.

529
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:07,650
You just tapped me from behind.

530
00:29:08,150 --> 00:29:09,690
You must've done
lots of wrong things.

531
00:29:10,490 --> 00:29:11,650
Speak for yourself.

532
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:12,960
Aren't we the same?

533
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,830
Don't be mad anymore.

534
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:17,790
I'll stop by after work today.

535
00:29:18,230 --> 00:29:20,000
(To Chairman Kang Gyu Cheol)

536
00:29:32,540 --> 00:29:35,310
(Director Do Min Jun is innocent!
Look into H and K Company.)

537
00:29:39,020 --> 00:29:40,880
(Chairman Kang Gyu Cheol)

538
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:43,020
Who put this envelope...

539
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:44,750
on my desk?

540
00:29:44,850 --> 00:29:46,860
It was just delivered here.

541
00:29:47,860 --> 00:29:51,290
Can you find the deliveryman
and bring him here?

542
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:55,230
Who gave you this envelope?

543
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:56,870
Some woman.

544
00:29:57,300 --> 00:30:00,170
I was just told to bring it here,
so I took it and brought it here.

545
00:30:00,970 --> 00:30:03,610
Then, where did you meet her...

546
00:30:03,610 --> 00:30:05,410
when you got this?

547
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:08,610
In front of the convenience store,
about 50m from here.

548
00:30:13,350 --> 00:30:14,520
(Letter of Resignation, Kim Do Yun)

549
00:30:14,520 --> 00:30:17,590
Dr. Park,
have you persuaded Dr. Kim?

550
00:30:18,690 --> 00:30:21,120
We can't lose our best surgeon.

551
00:30:24,490 --> 00:30:26,200
I haven't processed
his resignation yet,

552
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,660
so make sure you bring him back.

553
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:34,770
Have you found the punk
who snuck into my office...

554
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:35,770
and leaked the VIP record?

555
00:30:35,970 --> 00:30:38,610
Yes. The CCTV footage
taken in front of your office...

556
00:30:38,610 --> 00:30:40,580
didn't show his face
because of his cap,

557
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:43,910
but I confirmed him in the hallway
in front of the annex restroom.

558
00:30:43,910 --> 00:30:50,850
(Hanguk Hospital, Front of Restroom)

559
00:30:50,990 --> 00:30:52,590
Dr. Kim Do Yun.

560
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:56,430
This was why he resigned first
before I found out.

561
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:00,200
Come with us.

562
00:31:10,670 --> 00:31:17,210
(A Bell Convenience Store,
Kangrim-dong branch)

563
00:31:17,210 --> 00:31:19,450
Why did she have this delivered...

564
00:31:21,050 --> 00:31:23,220
instead of bringing it
to me directly?

565
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:36,900
(A Bell Convenience Store,
Kangrim-dong branch)

566
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:55,750
Hello? It's me.

567
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:59,420
I want to see you if you're free.

568
00:32:00,390 --> 00:32:02,330
Can you come to my office?

569
00:32:09,470 --> 00:32:10,530
Come in.

570
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:12,300
Excuse me.

571
00:32:14,470 --> 00:32:16,140
We met at the interview, right?

572
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:17,710
Hello, Director Kang.

573
00:32:18,340 --> 00:32:19,880
I remember you
because you were stunning.

574
00:32:21,210 --> 00:32:22,780
You were to begin next week,

575
00:32:22,910 --> 00:32:24,480
but I heard you were already here,
so I came to see you.

576
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:26,280
I wanted to settle in
before I got started.

577
00:32:28,790 --> 00:32:31,490
The chairman always wanted
to establish a clinic...

578
00:32:31,490 --> 00:32:33,620
in the office
as a part of employee benefits,

579
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:35,960
and his wish finally came true.

580
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:38,800
Please take good care
of YL Group's health,

581
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,800
both physically and mentally.

582
00:32:41,130 --> 00:32:43,270
Of course. If nothing else,
I'll make sure...

583
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,570
everyone stays healthy.

584
00:32:45,340 --> 00:32:47,200
Then, I'll see you next week.

585
00:32:57,780 --> 00:32:58,980
I'm almost here.

586
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:02,650
All right. I'll be there.

587
00:34:02,610 --> 00:34:06,520
(Queen's House)

588
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,550
Can you hold an investigation...

589
00:34:10,690 --> 00:34:11,990
on H and K Company?

590
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:16,030
And on Director Hwang Gi Chan.

591
00:34:18,160 --> 00:34:19,800
What did he give to Director Do?

592
00:34:21,430 --> 00:34:22,630
You cannot go inside.

593
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:25,130
You can't do this
without prior notification!

594
00:34:25,130 --> 00:34:27,440
A tax investigation began
by securing all files...

595
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:29,070
related to taxes and accounting.

596
00:34:29,310 --> 00:34:30,540
If I get asked for help,

597
00:34:31,240 --> 00:34:33,580
should I throw
a useless tactic first?

598
00:34:34,910 --> 00:34:36,150
I'm here, Mr. Chairman.

599
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:38,150
(Chairman Kang Gyu Cheol)
